claim.claim-text:
A staple cartridge, comprising:
(a) a body;
(b) a plurality of staples disposed in the body;
(c) a driver movably disposed in the body, wherein the driver is operable to drive the staples from the body; and
(d) a tray secured to the body, wherein the tray has a proximal end comprising at least one rigid tab, wherein the at least one rigid tab is sized and positioned to engage a portion of a cutting member of a stapling instrument to thereby prevent advancement of the cutting member through the body.
